### List all payments (default: 20 most recent)
GET http://localhost:8000/payments

### List payments filtered by status
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?status=succeeded

### List payments filtered by payment method
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?payment_method=card

### List payments filtered by merchant
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?merchant_code=TIENDA_SOL

### List payments filtered by provider
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?provider_code=STRIPE

### List payments filtered by currency
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?currency_code=EUR

### List payments with multiple filters
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?status=succeeded&payment_method=card&limit=5

### List payments with pagination (page 2)
GET http://localhost:8000/payments?limit=10&offset=10

### Generate 5 fake payments (default)
POST http://localhost:8000/payments/generate
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate 10 fake payments
POST http://localhost:8000/payments/generate?count=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate 1 fake payment
POST http://localhost:8000/payments/generate?count=1
Content-Type: application/json
